SMS
===

Hello this is my first pliugin that i save in Github

SMS plugin is a sms gateway with API suport from ClickAtell, next i will try to 
use another API

Example
=======

To use this plugin you must have API key from clickatell
after you get that, asign it in clickatell.yml in config folder

try to send sms in console

sms = SMS.new(CLICKATELL_CONFIG)

after that you just asign message and recipent in this line

sms.create(recipient, message_text)


